===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The passing of the sun directly overhead such that no shadows are cast by a pole sticking straight up, away from the center of the earth.  A Zenial Passage only occurs in locations between the tropic of cancer and the tropic of capricorn.  Zenial Passages were important to the Maya Civilization.

